Package: myCitation
Title: Find who cite my publication(s).
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Chun-Hui", "Gao", , "gaospecial@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-1445-7939"))
Description: Automatically fetch one's publication(s) and then the citation(s) of these publication(s). 
    After that, build a report of these citations automatically. These features are useful when one wants
    to evaluate his/her acadamic impact over the world. 
License: GPL3 + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
